{
  "texts": [
    "This table highlighting key metrics such as the table consists of Cluster ID is just a unique number for each group of documents.",
    "Size indicates about how many documents are in each cluster.",
    "Silhouette is a measure of the documents in a cluster are grouped together, with higher numbers being better.",
    "Latent Semantic Indexing (LSI) shows the main topic or keyword for each cluster.",
    "Log Likelihood Ratio (LLR) indicates how strongly the cluster is associated with its main topic."
  ]
}